Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,300)}{\c&HA0A0A0&}This story is fiction. The names of people,\Nplaces and groups are imaginary.\NObey traffic rules and drive safely.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.75,MainStyle,,0100,0000,0310,,{\bord0}INITIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Information, spreads in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we don't know how to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who say, "Money can't buy my love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.34,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...deserves a lariat three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.27,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We make love according to the manuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.24,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't notice the lack of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we suffocate, let's yell. Ho!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midnight dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,No place to relax in the sleepless city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:51.91,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We smile without dropping our guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:56.02,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to lie and the truth is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.07,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I desperately wanna shut and break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we gotta start.  Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.69,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move into the brand new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dive into the brand new trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:09.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of a big world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.94,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we go full speed and funky beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.57,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.52,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.42,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho! Here we go to an unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.17,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a newborn traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.22,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable footsteps are fun to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.32,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Get things done right, only when needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.84,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:30.14,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes, you'll receive slanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.18,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's warp uninteresting things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,..and lead at least a rational life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:35.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:43.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six of Akina will simply turn\Nto scraps of metal in a junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Now I'm pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He did that on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:39.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't lose to a lowlife\Nlike you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.53,0:02:50.75,MainStyle,,0140,0000,0128,,{\fad(500,900)}{\2a&HFF&}Angry Takumi's Maniacal Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't mind hitting the guardrail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And he used the reaction\Nto initiate his drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that Eight-Six driver thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six is gaining on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to kill himself, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eight-Six driver has gone nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If an ordinary driver gets angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:47.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...he'll keep making mistakes\Nand won't be able to run fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But he's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:57.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}His natural driving sense allows him\Nto push the Eight-Six to its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The angrier he gets, the faster he drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The result of this race is obvious, Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:19.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Although I'm pushing my EG6 to the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How could this be happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's strange{scary}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've never been so afraid of attacking\Nthe downhill before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's on my tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:08.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The EG6 is the best of its class, but it's\Nbeing pushed hard by an Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:12.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It has nothing to do with being fast or\Nslow, it's fundamentally different...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That Eight-Six is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:18.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But I'll be fine as long as\NI don't let him overtake me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}After I clear the five hairpin curves,\Nthe finish is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This battle is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't let you take the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is he going to hit me this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I thought he was going to hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...but what was that cornering just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:02.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He stayed inside at full speed,\Nand passed me so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How could I be overtaken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Takumi be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:26.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we have\Nto worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:31.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far, so he must've\Nfigured out this death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He might have pulled away from that EG6.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:41.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, that annoying jerk from the Night Kids\Nmust be sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:48.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be regretting challenging\NTakumi already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:06.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I dragged him into this\Ngumtape death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If I lose, I'll be the laughingstock\Nof the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll keep my reputation by\Nending this race with a tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:20.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The power of my B16A will make our cars run\Nside by side in this short straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}You can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The end of this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...will be a double crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One's coming!\NWhich one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be the EG6.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what's that Eight-Six's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He almost killed me.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The EG6 isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what happened to Shingo?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.82,0:09:58.57,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Hageshii yume jikan sae mo ima koeteku\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}The raging dream goes beyond time now.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.54,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Rage your dream, kaze no naka de mabushiku\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Rage your dream, shining bright in the wind...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.54,0:10:06.62,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}...sakebu anata yumetachi to\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}...you shout with your dream.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.62,0:10:10.64,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Rage your dream. kodou tomaru kurai ni\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Rage your dream. It almost stops my heartbeat.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.64,0:10:14.65,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}I can feel. Tsuyoku kanjiteru\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}I can feel it so strongly.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.65,0:10:18.64,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Rage your dream yami wo harisaite iku\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Rage your dream to break through the darkness.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.55,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Like a stream to the peak.\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Like a stream to the peak.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.55,0:10:26.60,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Sekai juu no kogoekitta yoru wo keshiteku\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}It will eliminate the frozen night.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.49,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}Rage your dream michi wo hiraiteku\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Rage your dream to explore the road.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.64,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}Di-ding dang another round, never slow down.\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Di-ding dang another round, never slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:37.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My EG6...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be Takumi...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky the damage isn't too severe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?\NAny injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:08.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quicker than calling an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:23.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stubborn.\NIt hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When we have an accident, we're\Nsupposed to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:35.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're locals, so we know\Nan emergency hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:39.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.  I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:47.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is that Eight-Six driver...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:10.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?!\NCome down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:18.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awake, 'cause it's that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:21.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come down, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:33.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've hit the car somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three scratches that look like the\Nkind made by touching the guardrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:45.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't drive it yesterday,\Nso it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those scratches\Non the bumper and fender!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:51.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.\NWhy'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:06.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I barely remember\Nhitting something with the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too young to be senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:18.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I raced this really disgusting guy yesterday,\Nand he pissed me off in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:23.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got really mad for some reason, but then\NI came home and went to bed quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:30.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how it happened, but you aren't\Nvery good if you hit something with your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been me, I wouldn't have hit\Nanything, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:44.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:18.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to do that, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The examination didn't show anything bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'll be leaving the hospital soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,These flowers are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Arigato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard all about it, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:41.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You won the gumtape death match!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're incredible, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can handle FR killer rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:57.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, I wanted to win that battle,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:01.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just because he pissed me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:04.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but also because I didn't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're becoming more and more\Nlike a Road Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's n...nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, once I get out of the hospital,\NI'll improve my technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:21.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That way I won't disgrace the name\Nof Akina's Levin/Trueno pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what about Saori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she doing fine?\NIs she alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she told me\Nto say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:40.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, once I'm out of the hospital,\Nlet's all go driving together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to know that Itsuki's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And his Eight-Five will be returned soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I... lied to him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:01.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori told me that she was really scared\Nwhen the accident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:05.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want to remember\Nthat moment, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:15.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even though she knows Itsuki's a nice guy,\Nshe wants to leave things behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:21.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori won't come after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers don't need a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:52.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take the car to a body shop, but\NI wanted to see your aged face before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:55.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi hit the car really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:59.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that race, it was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:08.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your car's fender is dented\Nand you're still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His driving style changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:15.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He was good, but he lacked something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to drive fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He broke through a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know, Bunta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know because I look at\Nthe Eight-Six every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:29.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how he drives so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop by on the way home, so\Nlet's have a drink later, Yuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:54.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A crazy son... and a crazy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:56.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.53,0:18:26.24,MainStyle,,0000,0350,0378,,{\c&HA0A0A0&\fs16\bord2}Kamameshi Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I couldn't help stopping the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:40.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't have any dirty thoughts,\Nbut I can't leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:06.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...I don't want you\Nto think I'm suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just curious about\Nwhat happened to your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:13.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:17.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried starting it many times,\Nbut the engine won't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:20.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NI appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:26.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In cases like this, it's probably\Nan electrical problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}S13...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Speedstars...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:58.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Man, I've never been so close to\Na woman other than my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:01.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Oh no, my heart's gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She's ultra cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:17.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm smelling a babe for the\Nfirst time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:22.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Oh no, what if I smell of sweat...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I think it'll run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the motor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It started!\NGreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:53.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.\NYou really saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:02.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire people who are\Ngood with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it up to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:11.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  You don't have to\Nworry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:21.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This could be the only chance God\Nwill give me in my entire life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Stupid, moron!\NI'm such an IDIOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sato Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.35,0:21:51.77,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}Mune ni nokoru nanigenai kotoba dakega\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Only casual words remained in my heart.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.97,0:22:01.01,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}Mayoi michi wo nukeru basho shitteita\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}I knew the place to free me from my delusion.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.01,0:22:09.65,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}Anata ni deatta hi kara nanika ga kawarihajimete\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Something started to change since the day I met you.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.40,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}Itsushika koko ni tatteita\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}I realized that I kept standing here.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.40,0:22:17.16,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}That's for your love.\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}That's for your love.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.16,0:22:25.95,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}Omoide ni kaeru hodo tsuyoi wake ja nai kedo\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}It wasn't a memory so strong to recall.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.95,0:22:29.20,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}Yorisotta ano koro ni\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}When we got close...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:15.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When I finally noticed, I had been\Nstanding dazed for thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:17.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:25.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I met an angel under\Na restaurant sign...{BTW, this sign and the restaurant does exist.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.08,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ai ni tsukarehate samayotte ta koro}Being tired of love, I wandered around...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:50.82,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita}...I lost myself to carnal desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:23:05.80,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kimagure na unmei wa mujaki na hitomi ni miserate yuku}Innocent eyes slowly charm my unpredictable fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.76,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sake bara no youni akaku}Bloom red like a rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.23,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku kimo wo daite}Strongly, strongly I hold you tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:21.19,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatta hitotsu kono omoi wo shinjitsu da to ieru}I can tell that only this feeling is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:26.06,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yorokobi wo kanadeyou}Let's play the melody of pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:30.89,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kagayaku mirai e}...into the bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:53.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah Kazoekirenai hodo tashikameaou}Let's make it sure over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:58.21,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Jounetu yo eien e todoke}This passion will be eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:02.18,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sake bara no youni akaku}Bloom red like a rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:05.72,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku dakishimete}Strongly, strongly I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:12.61,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatoe nani wo ushinattemo kono ude wo hanasanai}Even if I lose everything, I won't let your arm go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:17.49,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Utsukushiku Karen ni sake}Bloom beautifully and gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:22.93,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kiseki no hana yo}The flower of miracles.
