Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:34.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You appeared before me so suddenly,\Nlike a bright flash of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:38.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my heart to your beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.85,0:24:40.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Iketani, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.38,0:24:42.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.68,0:24:46.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a queen or an angel\Nwho fills my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.60,0:24:50.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.  He's completely\Nin his own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:53.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Initial D:\N"The Angels of Usui Mountain."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.22,0:24:54.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.37,0:24:56.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my sweet Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.83,0:24:58.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it!
