Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:24:59.93,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:24:59.93,MainStyle,,0060,0000,0190,,The Angels of Usui Mountain